<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="55" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1436,750,1026]" pageId="8" pageNumber="55">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,313,895,919]" pageId="8" pageNumber="55">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was briefly described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Cotte" box="[766,912,894,918]" pageId="8" pageNumber="55" refString="Cotte, J. (1924) Les cecidies des Alpes Maritimes et leurs producteurs. Memoire de la Societe Linneenne de Provence, Marseille, 3, 1 - 56 + 5 pls." type="journal article" year="1924">
Cotte (
<number box="[845,903,894,918]" pageId="8" pageNumber="55" value="1924.0">1924</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
who established it as a variety of 
<taxonomicName box="[1316,1428,894,918]" class="Arachnida" family="Eriophyidae" genus="Aceria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Prostigmata" pageId="8" pageNumber="55" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="drabae">
<emphasis box="[1316,1428,894,918]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="55">A. drabae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Later, 
<bibRefCitation author="Nalepa" box="[222,382,930,954]" pageId="8" pageNumber="55" refString="Nalepa, A. (1929) Neuer Katalog der bisher Beschriebenen Gallmilben, ihrer Gallen und Wirtspflanzen. Marcellia, 25 (1 - 4), 67 - 183." type="journal article" year="1929">
Nalepa (
<number box="[316,375,930,954]" pageId="8" pageNumber="55" value="1929.0">1929</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
associated this mite with flower deformation. 
<bibRefCitation author="Amrine" box="[900,1194,930,954]" pageId="8" pageNumber="55" refString="Amrine, J. W. Jr. &amp; Stasny, T. A. (1994) Catalog of the Eriophyoidea (Acarina: Prostigmata) of the World. Indira Publish. House, West Bloomfield, Michigan, USA, 804 pp." type="book" year="1994">
Amrine and Stasny (
<number box="[1127,1185,930,954]" pageId="8" pageNumber="55" value="1994.0">1994</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
elevated this name to the rank of species and treated it as a distinct species such as reported in the Fauna Europaea checklist (de 
<bibRefCitation author="Lillo" pageId="8" pageNumber="55" refString="de Lillo E. (2004) Fauna Europaea: Eriophyoidea. In: W. Magowski (Ed.) Fauna Europaea: Acariformes. Fauna Europaea version 1. 1, http: // www. faunaeur. org (access date 1 April 2011)" type="journal article" year="2004">
Lillo 
<number box="[151,212,1002,1026]" pageId="8" pageNumber="55" value="2004.0">2004</number>
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
